title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 19 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 19 2022
description:
Mar-a-Lago raid puts GOP on defense, distracts from Biden Administration failures. Does Merrick Garland have the stones to follow through, or will the Mar-a-Lago raid story fizzle out? The poster boy for Trump Derangement Syndrome: "Hunter literally could have had the corpses of children in his basement. I would not have cared." After the cancellation of Reliable Sources, CNN head honcho warns employees that more changes are coming. Stephen King laments the loss of Brian Stelter. What's the scariest movie you ever saw?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
